  "subject": "Allow rechecking a patchset about docs",
  "commit_message": "Allow rechecking a patchset about docs\n\nThe default regex in global jjb isn't not the classical one\n'^Patch Set\\s+\\d+:\\s+(recheck|reverify)\\s*$'\n\nIt overrides the triggers in the verify job to conform with\nthe classical gerrit recheck messages (see OPNFV, OpenStack, etc.).\n\nIssue-ID: DOC-782\n\nSigned-off-by: Cédric Ollivier <cedric.ollivier@orange.com>\nChange-Id: Ic1d319ecc5dfca399842512d37bec3506f443b42\n",
